text: German Šlein (born 28 March 1996) is an Estonian professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Estonian club Legion. ==Career== Šlein joined Flora in the summer 2013. He was loaned out to Czech club FC Vysočina Jihlava for the 2018-19 season. Ahead of the 2019-20 season, he was loaned out to JK Trans Narva but after playing one game for the club in the Europa League qualification due to an injury and returned to FC Flora.
